<!-- PJG STAG 4700 -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;907.20 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Content of homeownership plan. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The homeownership plan must address the following matters, as applicable to the particular factual situation: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(a) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Property description.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 A description of the property, including identification of the specific dwellings to be sold. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Plan for repair or rehabilitation.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 If applicable, a plan for any repair or rehabilitation required under &sect;907.6, based on the assessment of the
physical condition of the property that is included in the supporting documentation. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(c) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Selection of purchasers.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Purchaser eligibility and selection (see &sect;907.8). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(d) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Terms of sale.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Terms and conditions of sale (see, particularly, &sect;&sect;907.11 through 907.14). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(e) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Consultation plan.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 A plan for consultation with residents during the implementation stage (see &sect;907.5). If appropriate, this
may be combined with the plan for counseling. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(f) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Budget estimate.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 A budget estimate, showing the costs of implementing the plan, and the sources of the funds that will be used. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(g) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Counseling plan.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Counseling, training, and technical assistance to be provided in accordance with &sect;907.9. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(h) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Sale to entity other than residents.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 If the plan contemplates sale to residents via an entity other than the Housing Authority, a description of that entity's
responsibilities. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Plan for nonpurchasers.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 If applicable, a plan for nonpurchasing residents, in accordance with &sect;907.10. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(j) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Administrative plan.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 An administrative plan, including estimated staffing requirements. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(k) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Plan for use of sale proceeds.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 An estimate of the sale proceeds and an explanation of how they will be used, in accordance with &sect;907.15. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(l) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Accounting and reporting procedures.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 A description of the accounting and reporting procedures to be used, including those required to meet the requirements
of &sect;907.17. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(m) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Timetable.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 An estimated timetable for the major steps required to carry out the plan. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(n) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Affirmative Fair Housing Marketing Strategy.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 A description of the Housing Authority's strategy for informing and soliciting applications from people who are
least likely to apply, because of race, color, religion, sex, handicap, familial status, or national origin, for
the homeownership program without special outreach pursuant to &sect;907.7. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(o) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Supportive Services Plan.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 A description of the need for and availability of supportive services to be provided pursuant to &sect;907.9(a) as
well as the source and funding level for the supportive services to be provided. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG /STAG -->
</TEXT>
