<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 Steven C. Fox, Aerospace Engineer, Airframe Branch, ANM&hyph;120S, FAA, Transport Airplane Directorate, Seattle
Aircraft Certification Office, 1601 Lind Avenue, SW., Renton, Washington 98055&hyph;4056; telephone (206) 227&hyph;2777;
fax (206) 227&hyph;1181.
