Protection Agency, Region 9, Air and Toxics Division (A&hyph;2&hyph;1), Attention: Docket No. CA&hyph;93&hyph;IM&hyph;3,
75 Hawthorne Street, San Francisco, CA 94105. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The public hearing will be held in the auditorium of the Los Angeles Department of Water and Power Building, 111 North
Hope, Los Angeles, California 90012 (telephone: (415) 744&hyph;1500) from 1 p.m. to 5 p.m. and from 7 p.m. to 9 p.m.

