<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The Secretary proposes to amend title 34 of the Code of Federal Regulations by revising part 602 to read as follows:

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=56 g=1 f=1 -->
PART 602_SECRETARY'S PROCEDURES AND CRITERIA FOR THE RECOGNITION OF ACCREDITING AGENCIES 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=72 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart A_General Provisions 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=70 g=1 f=1 -->
Sec. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=26 g=1 f=1 -->
602.1&blank;Purpose. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.2&blank;Definitions. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.3&blank;Organization and membership. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.4&blank;Submission of information to the Secretary by recognized accrediting agencies. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=72 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart B_Recognition and Termination Procedures 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=26 g=1 f=1 -->
602.10&blank;Application for recognition. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.11&blank;Preliminary review by the Secretary. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.12&blank;Review by the National Advisory Committee on Institutional Quality and Integrity. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.13&blank;Review and decision by the Secretary. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.14&blank;Limitation, suspension, or termination of recognition. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.15&blank;Requests for reconsideration of the Secretary's decisions. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.16&blank;Appeals procedures. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
602.17&blank;Publication of list of recognized agencies. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=72 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart C_Criteria for Secretarial Recognition 
