<!-- PJG STAG 4702 -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The Secretary proposes to amend title 34 of the Code of Federal Regulations by adding a new part 667 to read as follows:

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=52 g=1 f=1 -->
PART 667_STATE POSTSECONDARY REVIEW PROGRAM 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=72 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart A_General 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=70 g=1 f=1 -->
Sec. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=26 g=1 f=1 -->
667.1&blank;Scope and purpose. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.2&blank;Definitions. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.3&blank;State agreement. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.4&blank;State postsecondary review entity. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.5&blank;Criteria the Secretary uses to refer institutions to a SPRE for review. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.6&blank;SPRE selection of institutions for review. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.7&blank;Notice to SPRE of Federal actions. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.8&blank;Institutions with locations in more than one State. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=72 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart B_Allotment Formula and Funding Procedures 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=26 g=1 f=1 -->
667.11&blank;Allotment formula. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.12&blank;Application for funds. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.13&blank;Approval of funding application. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.14&blank;Allowable costs and activities. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.15&blank;Fiscal procedures and records. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.16&blank;Supplement, not supplant, requirement. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=76 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart C_State Review Standards, SPRE Reviews, and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 Termination of Institutional Participation 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=26 g=1 f=1 -->
667.21&blank;State review standards. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.22&blank;Disapproval of State review standards. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
