<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
667.26&blank;Due process requirements. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=4 -->
Authority: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
20 U.S.C. 1099a through 1099a&hyph;3, unless otherwise noted. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=52 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart A_General 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;667.1 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Scope and purpose. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(a)(1) This part establishes the rules and procedures that govern the State Postsecondary Review Program, which
is authorized under Title IV, Part H, Subpart 1 of the Higher Education Act of 1965, as amended (HEA). The purpose of
the program is to strengthen State oversight of institutions participating in the Title IV, HEA programs through
the development of State standards for those institutions, and State review under those standards of institutions
referred by the Secretary under &sect;667.5 or selected by the State under &sect;667.6. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) Under this part, if a State finds that an institution it reviews does not satisfy the State standards, the State
may_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) Require the institution to take prompt actions to bring itself into compliance with the State's standards; or

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Determine that the institution should no longer participate in a Title IV, HEA program. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) A State must carry out activities under this part only to the extent that the costs of those activities will be reimbursed
by Federal funds. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(c) As used in this part, ``an institution'' includes_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) An institution of higher education as defined in 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
34 CFR 600.4; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) A proprietary institution of higher education as defined in 34 CFR 600.5; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) A postsecondary vocational institution as defined in 34 CFR 600.6. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(d) The provisions in the Education Department General Administrative Regulations, State Administered Programs,
34 CFR Part 76, do not apply to this part except for the provisions in_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) 34 CFR 76.1, 76.2, and 76.50 of subpart A; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) 34 CFR 76.500 through 76.534, 76.561, 76.563, and 76.580 through 76.592 of Subpart F; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) 34 CFR 76.700 through 76.702, 76.707, 76.720, 76.730, 76.731, 76.734, 76.760, and 76.761 of subpart G. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=20 g=1 f=1 -->
(Authority: 20 U.S.C. 1099a&hyph;1099a&hyph;3) 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;667.2 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Definitions. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(a) The following terms used in this part are defined in the regulations governing Institutional Eligibility under
the Higher Education Act of 1965, as amended, 34 CFR Part 600:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=25 g=1 f=1 -->
Branch campus 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Educational program 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Federal Family Education Loan (FFEL) programs 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Nationally recognized accrediting agency 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Recognized occupation 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Regular student 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Secretary 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(b) The following terms used in this part are defined in the Student Assistance General Provisions regulations, 34
CFR part 668: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=25 g=1 f=1 -->
Award year 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Clock hour 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Eligible program 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

